## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- We will run `gradlew build` in the `frontend` folder to ensure all Kotlin code compiles successfully.
- We will boot the backend API using `gradlew bootRun`.

### Manual Verification
- We will build and deploy the Android app to an emulator.
- We can manually test the registration flow by entering a name, email, password, and role, and checking if the backend receives the request and inserts the user into the local PostgreSQL database.
- We can test the login flow using the registered credentials.
